    "gnn_section": "ActInfPOMDP",
    "footer": "Deep Planning Horizon POMDP v1 - GNN Representation.\nT=5 horizon enables multi-step consequence reasoning.\nPolicy space grows exponentially with T: |actions|^T = 4^3 = 64 policies (pruned).",
